Highlights
                    

                      

                        
M1 | karrigan - 3 AK HS kills on the Mid offensive (initial frags)

                      

                      

                        
M1 | Patsi - 4 kills (3 Glock, USP-S HS) on the bombsite A offensive to turn a 2vs5 situation in favor of Spirit and secure them the second half pistol round win

                      

                      

                        
M1 | karrigan - 1vs3 clutch (CT - pre-plant situation) to bring FaZe on the verge of map point

                      

                      

                        
M1 | degster - 1vs2 clutch (T - bomb planted after 1 clutch kill) to keep FaZe off map point

                      

                      

                        
M1 | ropz - 1vs2 clutch (CT - post-plant situation) to secure the map victory for FaZe

                      

                      

                        
M2 | s1ren - quick 1vs2 clutch (T - post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | magixx - ACE (including 1vs1 clutch) to turn an initial 3vs5 situation (Part 1 - observer)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | magixx - ACE (including 1vs1 clutch) to turn an initial 3vs5 situation (Part 2 - REPLAY)

                      

                      

                        
M2 OT | Twistzz - 1vs3 clutch (T - post-plant situation) to keep Spirit off map point

                      

                      

                        
M2 OT | magixx - 1vs4 clutch (CT - post-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M2 OT | karrigan (CT) - jumping Knife kill on degster to secure the match victory for FaZe following a clean round
